'''TEOTWAWKI''' is an [[acronym]] standing for "'''T'''he '''E'''nd '''O'''f '''T'''he '''W'''orld '''A'''s '''W'''e '''K'''now '''I'''t". It is often seen in online [[survivalist]] groups, but has spread into somewhat more common usage.  It is particularily used by those people who are aware that Peak Oil is upon us.  Since energy is the basis for life, and cheap energy (ancient sunlight per Thom Hartmann) is the foundation of civilization, TEOTWAWKI is predicted to occur as various peaks of productions in oil, Natural Gas, coal and even soil fertility occur.  Fatalists as well as survivalists are discussing this on the web.  Some such as Richard Duncan say that an even more important peak has occurred - that being the peak of energy produced per capita.  He predicts that we are on the downward side and that the electric grid may soon collapse (Olduvai Theory)and with it civilization as we know it.  
  
See also [[End of the world]].

